==English==
===Adjective===
'''grumpy''' (''[[comparative]]'' '''grumpier''', ''[[superlative]]'' '''grumpiest''')

# [[unhappy]] and/or [[irritable]], a word which is particularly applied to babies and children or adults who are acting childishly.
#: ''Tommy feels '''grumpy''' today because his friend stole his ball.''

